com.sonf.filter

类 ProtocolFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sonf.core.filter.IFilterAdapter
      • com.sonf.filter.ProtocolFilter
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    IFilter

    public class ProtocolFilter
extends IFilterAdapter
    An filter which translates binary or protocol specific data into message objects and vice versa using IProtocolEncoder, or IProtocolDecoder.
